'''Bilafond Glacier''' ({{lang-ur|بلا فوند گلیشیر}}) is located in [[Siachen Glacier|Siachen region]] across [[Karakoram Range]] in [[Pakistan]].<ref>[http://tribune.com.pk/story/368394/the-fight-for-siachen/ The fight for Siachen]</ref> It is a main source for [[Saltoro River]].<ref name=Gulia>{{cite book|author=K.S. Gulia|title=Discovering Himalaya : Tourism of Himalaya Region|date=2 September 2007|publisher=Isha Books|isbn=978-8182054103|page=44|url=https://books.google.com/?id=ugFIz7ph-kEC&pg=PA44&dq=Bilafond+glacier#v=onepage&q=Bilafond%20glacier&f=false|accessdate=26 April 2012}}</ref> It is under Pakistani control.<ref>{{Cite book|url = https://books.google.com/books?id=YBykAwAAQBAJ|title = Snow and Ice-Related Hazards, Risks, and Disasters|last = Haeberli|first = Wilfried|last2 = Whiteman|first2 = Colin|date = 2014-10-27|publisher = Academic Press|isbn = 9780123964731|language = en}}</ref>

