arta sabrewing]]''' ||''Campylopterus phainopeplus'' || '''2500 – 9999'''<ref name='Campylopterus phainopeplus IUCN'>{{cite web | url = http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/106001841/0 | title = Campylopterus phainopeplus | accessdate = 2012-11-28 | author = [[BirdLife International]] | year = 2012 | work = [[IUCN Red List of Threatened Species]]. Version 2012.2 | publisher = [[IUCN]] }}</ref>||align=center style="background:#FAEB86"| [[Endangered species|EN]]<ref name='Campylopterus phainopeplus IUCN'/> || align=center|{{decrease}}<ref name='Campylopterus phainopeplus IUCN'/> || || |- | '''[[Schouteden's swift]]''' ||''Schoutedenapus schoutedeni'' || '''2500 – 9999'''<ref name='Schoutedenapus schoutedeni IUCN'>{{cite web | url = http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/106001738/0 | title = Schoutedenapus schoutedeni | accessdate = 2012-12-02 | author = [[BirdLife International]] | year = 2012 | work = [[IUCN Red List of Threatened Species]]. Version 2012.2 | publisher = [[IUCN]] }}</ref>||align=center style="background:#b0f4b0"| [[Vulnerable species|VU]]<ref name='Schoutedenapus schoutedeni IUCN'/> || align=center|{{decrease}}<ref name='Schoutedenapus schoutedeni IUCN'/> || || |- | '''[[Venezuelan sylph]]''' ||''Aglaiocercus berlepschi'' || '''2500 – 9999'''<ref name='Aglaiocercus berlepschi IUCN'>{{cite web | url = http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/160032190/0 | title = Aglaiocercus berlepschi | accessdate = 2012-11-28 | author = [[BirdLife International]] | year = 2012 | work = [[IUCN Red List of Threatened Species]]. Version 2012.2 | publisher = [[IUCN]] }}</ref>||align=center style="background:#FAEB86"| [[Endangered species|EN]]<ref name='Aglaiocercus berlepschi IUCN'/> || align=center|{{decrease}}<ref name='Aglaiocercus berlepschi IUCN'/> || || |- | '''[[Mariana swiftlet]]''' ||''Collocalia bartschi'' || '''3200 – 3500'''<ref name='Collocalia bartschi IUCN'>{{cite web | url = http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/160030057/0 | title = Collocalia bartschi | accessdate =